So ugh idk how to start this at all so here I go.
I played this server for a little bit a very long while back and recently remembered this server. Joining this server I discovered it has a teamspeak so I joined it and well the music bot was lit along with from what I saw that yesterday a great community. Only disappointment I had was the shop was removed the one with the items like the kb shovel and explosive bow etc.
well about me I'm 15, from Australia and well I guess I'll hardly meet any of you for a while because of timezones. Also I assume AMA means ask me anything judging by threads so yeah AMA
